Package com.Software.FitnessSystem.AdminControllers

Class ProgramEnrollment

java.lang.Object
com.Software.FitnessSystem.AdminControllers.ProgramEnrollment
public class ProgramEnrollment extends Object
Represents the enrollment statistics for a fitness program. This class contains information about the program's name, the number of enrollments, and the program's status (e.g., Active or Completed). It also provides utility methods to generate and manage enrollment statistics from a map of fitness programs.
Author:
Muath Hassoun
